  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to identify the most optimal therapy for Bowen's disease:
      excision versus Photodynamic therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The study is a randomized clinical trial in which two treatment options for Bowen's disease,
      excision and photodynamic therapy, are compared on recurrence rate, cosmesis en expenses.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
